      "span_text": "The biologically active secretoneurin fragment of human SCG2 (TNEIVEEQYTPQSLATLESVFQELGKLTGPNNQ) was measured by RIA, as previously described  with a rabbit polyclonal antibody directed against synthetic human secretoneurin (SCG2 154-165 ) and iodination on the endogenous Tyr."
